A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Occupational Licensing and Certification – Criminal History – Prohibited
3 Disclosures
4 FOR the purpose of altering certain provisions of law regarding the prohibition on certain
5 departments of State government denying an occupational license or certificate to an
6 applicant solely on the basis of the criminal history of the applicant to apply only to
7 the Maryland Department of Labor and prohibiting the department from requiring
8 disclosure of certain actions on an application; and generally relating to occupational
9 licensing and certification.
